file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Petstore
  license:
    name: MIT
  description: |
    This description is for testing
    multi-line
    description

servers:
  - url: http://petstore.swagger.io/v1
paths:
  /{supiOrSuci}/security-information-rg:
    get:
      summary: Get authentication data for the FN-RG
      operationId: GetRgAuthData
      tags:
        - Get Auth Data for FN-RG
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Null response
      parameters:
        - name: plmn-id
          in: query
          description: serving PLMN ID
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pet'
components:
  parameters:
    MyParam:
      name: foo
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
  securitySchemes:
    BearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
  schemas:
    Pet:
      required:
        - id
        - name
      properties:
        id:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        name:
          type: string
        tag:
          type: string
    Error:
      required:
        - code
        - message
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        message:
          type: string
    PetForm:
      title: PetForm
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        age:
          type: integer
